lyrics:
[verse]
In a world of magic and wonder, so grand
A boy named Harry, with a lightning scar in hand
He ventured to Hogwarts, his destiny untold
With friends by his side, they were brave and bold

[chorus]
Harry Potter, the chosen one so strong
Fighting against evil, where he belongs
With courage and loyalty, his magic will prevail
In Hogwarts Castle, where enchantments never fail
